\": 127, \"to\": 137}, {\"ngram\": \"the city's first marathon\", \"from\": 142, \"to\": 167}, {\"ngram\": \"TheDublin\", \"from\": 168, \"to\": 177}, {\"ngram\": \"an annual, inspiring and colourful fixture\", \"from\": 197, \"to\": 239}, {\"ngram\": \"the inaugural race\", \"from\": 277, \"to\": 295}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it may not have had the instant success were it not forBertie Messitt.\", \"from\": 308, \"to\": 382, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the instant success\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 351}, {\"ngram\": \"forBertie Messitt\", \"from\": 364, \"to\": 381}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From serving as a bus conductor on theNo.10 Dublin bus routeto drawing up the route for the marathon around the city, Messitt has had a huge impact on the history of Dublin marathon and Irish athletics.\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 585, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 427, \"end\": 437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_Bus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dublin bus\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_Bus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_Bus\"}, {\"begin\": 549, \"end\": 564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_Marathon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dublin marathon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_Marathon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_Marathon\"}, {\"begin\": 569, \"end\": 574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999993277444886, \"rank\": 6.675182981056438e-07, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bus conductor\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 414}, {\"ngram\": \"the route\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 466}, {\"ngram\": \"the marathon\", \"from\": 471, \"to\": 483}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 499}, {\"ngram\": \"Messitt\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 508}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge impact\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 530}, {\"ngram\": \"the history\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 545}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Born in Boghall, Bray in 1928, Messitt joined the British Army after the Second World War, where he took part in his first cross country race.\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 729, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 595, \"end\": 602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boghall\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Boghall\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boghall\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boghall\"}, {\"begin\": 637, \"end\": 649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Army\", \"score\": 0.9999998924236082, \"rank\": 1.0744140421008728e-07, \"text\": \"British Army\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Army\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Army\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Messitt\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 625}, {\"ngram\": \"the Second World War\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 676}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 696}, {\"ngram\": \"his first cross country race\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 728}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was posted in the Middle East and participated in one mile and three mile races.\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 813, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Middle East\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 762}, {\"ngram\": \"one mile and three mile races\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 812}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He began to race competitively upon his return to Ireland in the 1950s.\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 885, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 864, \"end\": 871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.8784462415710486e-14, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedi